record.title: MEASURE READ THE FIRST TIME--S.J. RES. 9

speaking.paragraph: Mr. President, S.J. Res. 9 is at the desk and I ask for its first reading.

record.chair: The clerk will report the joint resolution by title.
record.narrative: The legislative clerk read as follows:

speaking.paragraph: Mr. President, I ask for its second reading but object to my own request.

record.chair: Objection is heard. The joint resolution will receive its second reading on the next legislative day.
